    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sh-Polypeptide-56 Tripeptide-44 sh-Oligopeptide-1 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Polypeptide-56, sh-Oligopeptide-1 and Tripeptide-44. The fused peptide contains 1060 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
